## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="7e14a-159">Se o <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AxisScaleBreakStyle.StartFromZero%2A> está definida como <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.StartFromZero.Auto>, o gráfico calcula automaticamente se deseja iniciar o mínimo de escala do eixo y do menor valor da série ou do zero.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7e14a-159">If the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AxisScaleBreakStyle.StartFromZero%2A> property is set to <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.StartFromZero.Auto>, the chart will automatically calculate whether to start the Y-axis scale minimum from the lowest value in the series or from zero.</span></span>  
  
   
  
